result.title: Zainab Johnson: Hijabs Off
result.author: All Things Comedy, Amazon Studios
result.description: Zainab Johnson is a gifted and daring comedian who effortlessly blends relatable stories, sharp wit, and thought-provoking social commentary into her unique style of stand-up comedy. Her debut special explores her identity as a Black female Muslim, having 12 siblings, and growing up in Harlem.
